<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ITA10">
<l>pērttaṉai mācakaṭam piḷḷaiyāy maṇṇirantu</l>
<l>kāttaṉai palluyiruṅ kāvalaṉē – yēttiya</l>
<l>nāvuṭaiyēṉ pūvuṭaiyē ṉiṉṉuḷḷi niṉṟamaiyāṟ</l>
<l>kāvaṭiyēṉ paṭṭa kaṭai</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Me who has a [skilful] tongue</l>
<l>that praised as the guardian of many lives, him who as a child</l>
<l>destroyed the horse cart, who begged for [and] protected the earth,</l>
<l>	me with flowers, for thinking of you constantly,</l>
<l>protect [me] who am [your] servant, at the end that comes.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
